parameters.text:
=🚀 High Intent Lead Detected!

Company: {{$json.domain}}

Intent Score: {{$json.intent_score}}

Signals Breakdown:
- Hiring Activity: {{$json.hiring_signal}}
- Tech Adoption: {{$json.tech_signal}}
- News Mentions: {{$json.news_signal}}

Insight:
This company is showing strong buying signals based on recent activity. Highly recommended for immediate outreach.

Next Action:
Reach out to this prospect ASAP while intent is high.

parameters.jsCode:
return items.map((item, index) => {

  // ✅ Jobs count
  const jobs = $items("Fetch Job Openings")[index]?.json?.data?.length || 0;

  // ✅ Tech count
  const tech = $items("Fetch Tech Stack")[index]?.json?.data?.length || 0;

  // ✅ News count (current node input)
  const news = item.json.data?.length || 0;

  // ✅ Domain (from Google Sheet - correct source)
  const domain = $items("Get Prospect List")[index]?.json?.domain || "unknown";

  // ✅ Final scoring logic
  const score = (jobs * 5) + (tech * 3) + (news * 2);

  return {
    json: {
      domain,
      hiring_signal: jobs,
      tech_signal: tech,
      news_signal: news,
      intent_score: score
    }
  };
});
